
                        Angular - Front end technology

                    Basic Commands :-
                
        1. create a project - ng new project-name
        2. to run Angular project - ng serve
        3. to generete new project - ng g c component-name



                                Basic Concepts

        1. module - To import libraries
                  - angular have Atleast one module
        2. component - to generate ts, css,bootstrap - AppComponent                   ts file     - component
        3. Data binding - sharing data within a component                             html file   -  view

                3.1 one way binding - only single direction sharing
                    3.1.1   component to view

                        3.1.1.1 String interpolation - {{variable-name}}
                        3.1.1.2 Property binding   -  [tag attribute]="class-property"

                    3.1.2   view to component

                        3.1.2.1  Event binding - (event-name)="function-call"
                        3.1.2.2  Event binding using $event - (event-name)="function-call($event)"
                        3.1.2.3  Template arferencing variable - syntax:  #variable-name